{"tid":1443102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我發現搞地區文宣 一定要有地區色彩","createTime":"2019-08-11T06:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:06:29.000Z","uid":94771,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ec4d92e7dd57930e3bec4a25cbeb1927780ef4","tid":1443102,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"有一個方法 可以令文宣更有宣傳力<br />\n就係文宣可以有地區特色 即係文宣加返係個個區發生的事<br />\n<br />\n就警暴來講<br />\n大埔區的文宣有大埔發生的警暴事件<br />\n沙田區的文宣有沙田發生的警暴事件<br />\n黃大仙區的文宣有黃大仙發生的警暴事件<br />\n<br />\n因為個文宣講的野同居住地方好接近 好多人都會有種吸引力去睇 因為覺得可能殺到埋身<br />\n<br />\n<strong>打個比如 :<br />\n如果你係沙田派黃大仙發生的事 吸引力真係唔夠多 因為覺得唔關自己事<br />\n但如果有少少關沙田的事再用件事放返去黃大仙 咁睇的人就會關注好多</strong><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望派文宣的手足可以係文宣加返少少社區特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e7e22317625149bda558f04c3d76e86a07fef9","tid":1443102,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"青衣有咩色彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e805eeb60be208198111e23bcedd99aa80ced698","tid":1443102,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9C1v69v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9C1v69v.png&h=39bf046d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86ca699416af328032242f55ecb08c5cb9624bff","tid":1443102,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e7e22317625149bda558f04c3d76e86a07fef9","tid":1443102,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"青衣有咩色彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:40:43.000Z","msg":"無就照文宣住先<br />\n搵個方向<br />\n有就可以諗下依個方法"},{"pid":"0d07007db4c95486f521608621ba38547546756c","tid":1443102,"uid":94771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"re